name: #2-1 Ratree (The Four Fairies)
description:
This is a separate sub-collection of my Dream Dolls Collection. Glad to introduce "Ratree".

Today I dream of Ratree. Ratree is one of the four dolls that appear in the Four Fairies. (The Dream Dolls Collection) that first appeared in this special collection.

She had black hair full of glittering stars. She made my dreams extraordinarily beautiful tonight because she brought with me the beautiful starlight in the world of the Four Fairy. Even though it was night ,my dreams were bright and memorable.
